oai_dc:dc.dc:description: "Miss J.A. Scott, -- Rossville, -- Tennessee. -- I appreciate your -- Christmas post- -- card so nicely -- and thank you for it -- I called on you just -- before you left here -- but found you out and -- had no card with me. -- Trust you are well - -- Cordially, -- Maud J. Cowan"
